1997;;The Midas Touch;;American;;Peter Manoogian;;Trever O'Brien;;fantasy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Midas_Touch_(1997_film);;Drama about a 12-year-old boy who fantasises about having enough money to be able to cure his grandmother's serious heart condition. When he finds himself in a haunted house, the mysterious owner 'grants' him one wish - the Midas touch. The boy soon learns that it is more of a curse than a blessing when everything he touches turns into gold.